values: lol ok so i got rid of the livejournal cuz i was never online or posting or whatever, but guess what. it's backkkkkkkkk :) i cant really think of anything of importance to write about but it's like midnight, just got home, n im bored. my life has been pretty great the past couple months. well sorta.... i mean after cheering i realized that i kinda fucked my grades up pretty bad by not attending classes.... i was failin a class or 2 but i got those back up. i was worried i wasnt going to graduate (and therefore be stuck in the illinios valley for the rest of my life) BUT i found out today that I am gonna graduate, and im graduating with honors. :) exciting. lol i guess working my ass off payed off! WIU here i come... (MCNALLY I CANT WAIT!!!!!) other than that im still working at good old delaneys. weekends only for now. but im sure my schedule's gonna change soon which should be good if they give me more days. im also workin for my dad this summer. drivin a differnt car all the time n getting payed for it? umm yes please? other than that i just be hanging out with my friends alot lately. im so pumped that everyones back from school. kat although sux because she's moving back up to the city in 2 weeks. (love u anyway girl! lol i'll come hide in chicago alot this summer IM SURE!) me n sarah rae are going to see trick pony in like a week (may 29th i think it is?) so that will be SOOOO much fun! lol especially since like everyone is going :) ummm maybe a dave concert this summer?!?!?!? scrouchy?!?!?! lol can i go to dave with you!??!?!?! im tryin... dunno how thats gonna work out. im really in need of a road trip soon.(im thinkin chicago sounds fun....) like with my friends lets get crunk road trip. not this whole going to mertle beach with the folks thing. im not really lookin forward to that, but i mean i guess it could be cool. maybe some fine ass boys? lol who knows! deffinatley not sure whats going on this weekend. tomorrow i plan on being fucked up. preferably before the graduation ceremony (yes im a dork i have to go to the ceremony). but i doubt that it'll happen. lol but im sure if i post on saturday u'll be able to read about me being drunk n all the stupid things im sure to do! im actually really lookin forward to summer!! lol really pissed that im gonna be missin title series races though cuz i'll be in mertle beach... but nationals? lol oh yah... lets hope that turns out as great as last year!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! my boys are coming back!!! :) lol anyway enough of my rambling. im gonna go get some sleep!

1) I'm gonna write a book called "the games people play" which i think might already be a book or something cuz it sounds familiar, but for reals. i've noticed lately how many differnt frickin games people have been playin with each other. and the sad thing is that i've realized i've been doin it alot myself! it's rediculous
